            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EAbraham's%20sacrifice%20of%20Isaac%20represents%20a%20faith%20that%20acts%2C%20not%20one%20that%20just%20talks.%20Anyone%20can%20say%2C%20%22I%20trust%20the%20Lord%2C%22%20but%20raising%20a%20knife%20to%20one's%20most%20precious%20possession%20is%20proof%20of%20real%20faith.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20only%20hear%20the%20commandments%20of%20God-we%20must%20do%20them.%20James%20said%2C%20%22Fool!%20When%20will%20you%20ever%20learn%20that%20faith%20that%20does%20not%20result%20in%20good%20deeds%20is%20useless%3F%22%20(James%202%3A20).%20There%20comes%20a%20moment%20in%20our%20lives%20when%20we%20must%20translate%20talk%20into%20an%20action%20that%20demonstrates%20the%20reality%20of%20our%20faith.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAs%20Abraham%20climbed%20the%20mountain%20of%20Moriah%2C%20his%20faith%20gave%20energy%20to%20his%20actions.%20In%20his%20mind%20he%20had%20reckoned%20that%20God%20was%20able%20to%20raise%20up%20Isaac%2C%20even%20if%20he%20died%20(Hebrews%2011%3A19).%20Abraham's%20faith%20risked%20all%20and%20lost%20nothing.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELet's%20step%20out%20in%20obedience.%20When%20we%20do%2C%20God%20will%20have%20the%20ram%20waiting%20in%20the%20thicket!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Genesis.20:1-22:24",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EGenesis%2020%3A1-22%3A24%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_1%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EGenesis%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EAbraham%20Deceives%20Abimelech%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EAbraham%20moved%20south%20to%20the%20Negev%20and%20lived%20for%20a%20while%20between%20Kadesh%20and%20Shur%2C%20and%20then%20he%20moved%20on%20to%20Gerar.%20While%20living%20there%20as%20a%20foreigner%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_2%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EAbraham%20introduced%20his%20wife%2C%20Sarah%2C%20by%20saying%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BShe%20is%20my%20sister.%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20King%20Abimelech%20of%20Gerar%20sent%20for%20Sarah%20and%20had%20her%20brought%20to%20him%20at%20his%20palace.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_3%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20that%20night%20God%20came%20to%20Abimelech%20in%20a%20dream%20and%20told%20him%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYou%20are%20a%20dead%20man%2C%20for%20that%20woman%20you%20have%20taken%20is%20already%20married!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_4%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20Abimelech%20had%20not%20slept%20with%20her%20yet%2C%20so%20he%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLord%2C%20will%20you%20destroy%20an%20innocent%20nation%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_5%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EDidn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20Abraham%20tell%20me%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BShe%20is%20my%20sister%26%23x2019%3B%3F%20And%20she%20herself%20said%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BYes%2C%20he%20is%20my%20brother.%26%23x2019%3B%20I%20acted%20in%20complete%20innocence!%20My%20hands%20are%20clean.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_6%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20the%20dream%20God%20responded%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYes%2C%20I%20know%20you%20are%20innocent.%20That%26%23x2019%3Bs%20why%20I%20kept%20you%20from%20sinning%20against%20me%2C%20and%20why%20I%20did%20not%20let%20you%20touch%20her.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_7%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20return%20the%20woman%20to%20her%20husband%2C%20and%20he%20will%20pray%20for%20you%2C%20for%20he%20is%20a%20prophet.%20Then%20you%20will%20live.%20But%20if%20you%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20return%20her%20to%20him%2C%20you%20can%20be%20sure%20that%20you%20and%20all%20your%20people%20will%20die.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_8%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EAbimelech%20got%20up%20early%20the%20next%20morning%20and%20quickly%20called%20all%20his%20servants%20together.%20When%20he%20told%20them%20what%20had%20happened%2C%20his%20men%20were%20terrified.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_9%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Abimelech%20called%20for%20Abraham.%20%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20have%20you%20done%20to%20us%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20demanded.%20%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20crime%20have%20I%20committed%20that%20deserves%20treatment%20like%20this%2C%20making%20me%20and%20my%20kingdom%20guilty%20of%20this%20great%20sin%3F%20No%20one%20should%20ever%20do%20what%20you%20have%20done!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_10%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EWhatever%20possessed%20you%20to%20do%20such%20a%20thing%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_11%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EAbraham%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20thought%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20a%20godless%20place.%20They%20will%20want%20my%20wife%20and%20will%20kill%20me%20to%20get%20her.%26%23x2019%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_12%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20she%20really%20is%20my%20sister%2C%20for%20we%20both%20have%20the%20same%20father%2C%20but%20different%20mothers.%20And%20I%20married%20her.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_13%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20God%20called%20me%20to%20leave%20my%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20home%20and%20to%20travel%20from%20place%20to%20place%2C%20I%20told%20her%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BDo%20me%20a%20favor.%20Wherever%20we%20go%2C%20tell%20the%20people%20that%20I%20am%20your%20brother.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_14%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Abimelech%20took%20some%20of%20his%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20cattle%2C%20and%20male%20and%20female%20servants%2C%20and%20he%20presented%20them%20to%20Abraham.%20He%20also%20returned%20his%20wife%2C%20Sarah%2C%20to%20him.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_15%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Abimelech%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLook%20over%20my%20land%20and%20choose%20any%20place%20where%20you%20would%20like%20to%20live.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_16%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20he%20said%20to%20Sarah%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLook%2C%20I%20am%20giving%20your%20%26%23x2018%3Bbrother%26%23x2019%3B%201%2C000%20pieces%20of%20silver%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E20%3A16%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E1%2C000%20%5Bshekels%5D%20of%20silver%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%2025%26%23xA0%3Bpounds%20or%2011.4%26%23xA0%3Bkilograms%20in%20weight.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20all%20these%20witnesses.%20This%20is%20to%20compensate%20you%20for%20any%20wrong%20I%20may%20have%20done%20to%20you.%20This%20will%20settle%20any%20claim%20against%20me%2C%20and%20your%20reputation%20is%20cleared.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_17%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Abraham%20prayed%20to%20God%2C%20and%20God%20healed%20Abimelech%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20and%20his%20female%20servants%2C%20so%20they%20could%20have%20children.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_20_18%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20caused%20all%20the%20women%20to%20be%20infertile%20because%20of%20what%20happened%20with%20Abraham%26%23x2019%3Bs%20wife%2C%20Sarah.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_21_1%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EGenesis%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Birth%20of%20Isaac%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20kept%20his%20word%20and%20did%20for%20Sarah%20exactly%20what%20he%20had%20promised.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_21_2%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EShe%20became%20pregnant%2C%20and%20she%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20son%20for%20Abraham%20in%20his%20old%20age.%20This%20happened%20at%20just%20the%20time%20God%20had%20said%20it%20would.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_21_3%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20Abraham%20named%20their%20son%20Isaac.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_21_4%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EEight%20days%20after%20Isaac%20was%20born%2C%20Abraham%20circumcised%20him%20as%20God%20had%20commanded.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_21_5%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EAbraham%20was%20100%26%23xA0%3Byears%20old%20when%20Isaac%20was%20born.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_21_6%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20Sarah%20declared%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BGod%20has%20brought%20me%20laughter.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E21%3A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20name%20%3Cem%3EIsaac%3C%2Fem%3E%20means%20%26%23x201C%3Bhe%20laughs.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%20All%20who%20hear%20about%20this%20will%20laugh%20with%20me.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_21_7%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EWho%20would%20have%20said%20to%20Abraham%20that%20Sarah%20would%20nurse%20a%20baby%3F%20Yet%20I%20have%20given%20Abraham%20a%20son%20in%20his%20old%20age!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_21_8%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EHagar%20and%20Ishmael%20Are%20Sent%20Away%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Isaac%20grew%20up%20and%20was%20about%20to%20be%20weaned%2C%20Abraham%20prepared%20a%20huge%20feast%20to%20celebrate%20the%20occasion.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_21_9%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20Sarah%20saw%20Ishmael%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20son%20of%20Abraham%20and%20her%20Egyptian%20servant%20Hagar%26%23x2014%3Bmaking%20fun%20of%20her%20son%2C%20Isaac.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E21%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%20and%20Latin%20Vulgate%3B%20Hebrew%20lacks%20%3Cem%3Eof%20her%20son%2C%20Isaac.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_21_10%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20she%20turned%20to%20Abraham%20and%20demanded%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BGet%20rid%20of%20that%20slave%20woman%20and%20her%20son.%20He%20is%20not%20going%20to%20share%20the%20inheritance%20with%20my%20son%2C%20Isaac.%20I%20won%26%23x2019%3Bt%20have%20it!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3